30
00:17:05,775 --> 00:17:09,696
-Kam greš?
-Po Eve.

31
00:17:10,447 --> 00:17:11,573
Ne hodi.

32
00:17:20,248 --> 00:17:22,083
Zakaj?

33
00:17:26,087 --> 00:17:30,258
So že bili pri njej.

34
00:17:56,451 --> 00:17:58,453
Potrebuješ kaj?

35
00:17:59,829 --> 00:18:00,997
Denar?

36
00:18:04,626 --> 00:18:10,215
-Dovolj imam.
-Ja, zdaj je samo tvoj.

37
00:20:13,088 --> 00:20:15,048
Kam?

38
